150 public bool TryStartForMouse(Player player)
151 {

153 _slot = -1;

157 return true;

160 public void Clear()
161 {
162 _shouldFastUse = false;

164
165 public bool CanFastUse()
166 {
167 if (!_shouldFastUse)
168 {
169 return false;
170 }
171 if (_isMouseItem)
172 {
173 return Main.mouseItem.type == _itemType;
174 }
175 return _player.inventory[_slot].type == _itemType;
176 }
177
178 public void EndFastUse()
179 {
180 if (_shouldFastUse)
181 {
182 if (!_isMouseItem && _player.inventory[_slot].IsAir)
183 {
184 Utils.Swap(ref Main.mouseItem, ref _player.inventory[_slot]);
185 }
186 Clear();
187 }
188 }

606 public static void Load()
607 {
608 if (!Main.InputProfiles.Load())
609 {
610 return;
611 }
612 Dictionary<string, PlayerInputProfile> dictionary = new Dictionary<string, PlayerInputProfile>();
613 string currentValue = null;
614 Main.InputProfiles.Get("Selected Profile", ref currentValue);
615 List<string> allKeys = Main.InputProfiles.GetAllKeys();
616 for (int i = 0; i < allKeys.Count; i++)
617 {
618 string text = allKeys[i];
619 if (text == "Selected Profile" || string.IsNullOrEmpty(text))
620 {
621 continue;
622 }
623 Dictionary<string, object> currentValue2 = new Dictionary<string, object>();
624 Main.InputProfiles.Get(text, ref currentValue2);
625 if (currentValue2.Count > 0)
626 {
627 PlayerInputProfile playerInputProfile = new PlayerInputProfile(text);
628 playerInputProfile.Initialize(PresetProfiles.None);
629 if (playerInputProfile.Load(currentValue2))
630 {
631 dictionary.Add(text, playerInputProfile);
632 }
633 }
634 }
635 if (dictionary.Count > 0)
636 {
637 Profiles = dictionary;
638 if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(currentValue) && Profiles.ContainsKey(currentValue))
639 {
640 SetSelectedProfile(currentValue);
641 }
642 else
643 {
644 SetSelectedProfile(Profiles.Keys.First());
645 }
646 }

1948 public static string BuildCommand(string CommandText, bool Last, params List<string>[] Bindings)
1949 {
1950 string text = "";
1951 if (Bindings.Length == 0)
1952 {
1953 return text;
1954 }
1955 text += GenerateGlyphList(Bindings[0]);
1956 for (int i = 1; i < Bindings.Length; i++)
1957 {
1958 string text2 = GenerateGlyphList(Bindings[i]);
1959 if (text2.Length > 0)
1960 {
1961 text = text + "/" + text2;
1962 }
1963 }
1964 if (text.Length > 0)
1965 {
1966 text = text + ": " + CommandText;
1967 if (!Last)
1968 {
1969 text += " ";
1970 }
1971 }
1972 return text;
1973 }
